### Create a room
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/rooms HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "testRoom",
    "creatorId": "81e3bf5c-0e52-48e5-8678-ec43070fdb6f",
    "type": "GROUP",
    "members": [
        { "userId": "66e099cd-e6e6-4b10-9649-59cf8e731941", "role": "MEMBER" }
    ]
}
